  "description": "A simple mod that adds blocks and panels for letters",
  "body": "<center>\n<a href='https://fabricmc.net'><img alt=\"Supported on Fabric Loader\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/cozy?gradientStart=dbd0b4&gradientEnd=aea694&lineOne=Supported%20on&lineTwo=Fabric%20Loader&colourOne=ffffff&colourTwo=dfdfa5&iconUrl=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/FabricMC/fabric-loader/refs/heads/master/src/main/resources/ui/icon/fabric_x128.png&format=svg\"></a>\n<a href='https://quiltmc.org'><img alt=\"Supported on Quilt Loader\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/cozy?gradientStart=271f33&gradientEnd=1c1526&lineOne=Supported%20on&lineTwo=Quilt%20Loader&colourOne=ffffff&colourTwo=dc29dd&iconUrl=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/QuiltMC/quilt-loader/refs/heads/develop/src/main/resources/ui/icon/quilt_x128.png&format=svg\"></a>\n</center>\nProvides placable panels that display text. There is one for each letter of the alphabet, one for \"-\" and one for \".\"\n\nThey will be obtainable in survival but currently aren't.\n\n# Current Sets\n- Magic Slate\n\n## Join my [Discord](https://discord.gg/B6bMWPbQyj) for support.",
